{"tid":1190211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子西貢被青蛇咬腳 再遇交通意外翻車傷","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T09:24:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf43dfc9a0166acb00ba84f5111a9cbcef871e0","tid":1190211,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"早上10時44分，西貢伙頭墳洲香港晨曦會戒毒所兩名男院友，在院舍內除草期間，其中一人被青蛇咬傷腳，另一院友見狀報警，約半小時後，院友用單車載送事主往碼頭等候救援期間，單車與一部運泥車相撞，共5人受傷，其中包括被蛇咬傷腳的男事主及載他往碼頭的院友，男事主可謂禍不單行，他仍然清醒，腳部淌血，最後他與友儕先由政府飛行服務隊吊送往東區醫院救治，其餘3名車禍中傷者輕傷，送到水警東基地，再由救護車送往將軍澳醫院治理。"},{"pid":"c9c619535a65adf12988251b21468c9cabe9e6f1","tid":1190211,"uid":73340,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMAfNBQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMAfNBQ.png&h=10e66ce3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8f550c359754313619fc7fc86e1349491192747","tid":1190211,"uid":157000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"地獄黑仔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7397e13cfb933db238fdbb686ac68906dc9e54","tid":1190211,"uid":24282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"耐人尋味"},{"pid":"4f4bb2ee22d2b7ded7b9d2c38462df8ba433eef0","tid":1190211,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"執返條命都算係咁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb49fd39e1e9d1d30221b2a1f38c60849ea25292","tid":1190211,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"老夫子朋友"},{"pid":"472b62642971c052ab357354c68429d7149cfe7a","tid":1190211,"uid":257567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"單車與泥頭車相撞   <span style=\"color: red;\">五人</span>受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj